                GNU gettext message catalogue
                GutenPalm zTXT
                HTML document
                ISO-8859 text
                JPEG image data
                Microsoft Reader eBook Data
                Microsoft Windows HtmlHelp Data
                Microsoft Word 2007+
                Mobipocket E-book
                MS Windows HtmlHelp Data
                Netpbm PPM data
                OpenDocument Text
                Pascal source
                PDF document
                PeanutPress PalmOS
                Perl script text
                PNG image data
                POSIX shell script text
